      #GtkFileChooser functions.
    </para>

@GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ERROR_NONEXISTENT: Indicates that a file does not exist.
@GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ERROR_BAD_FILENAME: Indicates a malformed filename.

